  "texts": [
    "BERT's architecture focuses on learning deep bidirectional representations from text, considering context from both sides.",
    "The 'base' version contains 12 transformer layers, each outputting a 768-dimensional hidden state, and is trained on lowercase text (uncased).",
    "This model is widely used in NLP tasks like question answering and sentiment analysis.",
    "BERT was fine-tuned by employing the OSDG Community Dataset, incorporating targets and indicators for each goal 50.",
    "For goals lacking text, relevant expressions from policies were used."
